  "reviews": "\u201cThis is a gem with the neglected rolling ball games.\u201d<br>8/10 \u2013 <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.4players.de/4players.php/dispbericht/PC-CDROM/Test/37388/82001/0/Road_to_Ballhalla.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >4Players</a></a><br><br>\u201cAn inventive and joyus ride. Or should I say... roll?\u201d<br>9/10 \u2013 <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.bitcultures.com/road-to-ballhalla-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >BitCultures</a></a><br><br>\u201cI never had so many laughs and good fun throughout my time playing this type of game as I did with Road To Ballhalla.\u201d<br>9/10 \u2013 <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://hardknockgamers.com/review-road-ballhalla/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >HardKnockGamers</a></a><br>",
